<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>智潮 AI - 专业人工智能资讯平台</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Noto+Serif+SC:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        
        :root {
            --brand: #D4622A;
            --brand-dark: #b8501e;
            --bg: #FFFAF3;
            --bg-card: #fff;
            --text: #1a1a1a;
            --text-secondary: #666F7D;
            --border: #e0d6c8;
            --border-light: #ece4d8;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: "Noto Sans CJK SC", "Noto Sans SC", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
        
        /* ===== TICKER ===== */
        .ticker-bar {
            background: #2c2c2c;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 13px;
            overflow: hidden;
            white-space: nowrap;
            height: 40px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #444;
        }
        .ticker-label {
            background: var(--brand);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 0 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 12px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .ticker-content {
            display: flex;
            animation: ticker-scroll 45s linear infinite;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .ticker-content span { padding-right: 60px; color: #ccc; }
        .ticker-content span::before { content: "•"; color: var(--brand); margin-right: 12px; }
        @keyframes ticker-scroll { 0% { transform: translateX(0); } 100% { transform: translateX(-50%); } }
        
        /* ===== HEADER ===== */
        header {
            background: #fff;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            box-shadow: 0 1px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
        }
        .header-inner {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            height: 64px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-family: "Noto Serif CJK SC", "Noto Serif SC", serif;
            font-size: 30px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--brand);
            text-decoration: none;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .logo span {
            color: var(--text);
            font-family: "Noto Sans CJK SC", sans-serif;
            font-weight: 300;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-left: 2px;
        }
        
        /* Nav tabs */
        nav { display: flex; gap: 4px; align-items: center; }
        nav a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #555;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 500;
            padding: 8px 18px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            position: relative;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        nav a:hover { color: var(--brand); background: rgba(212,98,42,0.05); }
        nav a.active {
            color: var(--brand);
            font-weight: 600;
            background: rgba(212,98,42,0.08);
        }
        nav a.active::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -1px;
            left: 18px;
            right: 18px;
            height: 3px;
            background: var(--brand);
        }
        .header-search {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            padding: 6px 14px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            background: #f8f5f0;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #999;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-left: 12px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .header-search:hover { border-color: var(--brand); }
        
        /* ===== SECTION SYSTEM ===== */
        .page-section { display: none; }
        .page-section.active { display: block; }
        
        /* ===== HERO ===== */
        .hero { margin-bottom: 40px; }
        .hero-card {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            overflow: hidden;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: box-shadow 0.3s;
        }
        .hero-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .hero-image {
            height: 400px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .hero-image.with-img {
            background: url('img/hero-ai.png') center/cover no-repeat;
        }
        .hero-image.with-img::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(26,26,46,0.5) 0%, rgba(212,98,42,0.2) 100%);
        }
        .hero-image::after {
            content: "AI · 未来";
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 30px;
            left: 30px;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
            font-size: 14px;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .hero-date-badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: 24px;
            left: 24px;
            background: var(--brand);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            z-index: 1;
            line-height: 1.4;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .hero-date-badge .day { font-size: 24px; display: block; }
        .hero-date-badge .month { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        .hero-content { padding: 48px 40px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; }
        .hero-tag {
            font-size: 13px;
            background: var(--brand);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }
        .hero-title {
            font-family: "Noto Serif CJK SC", serif;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            line-height: 1.35;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .hero-excerpt { font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 24px; }
        .hero-meta { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; font-size: 13px; color: #999; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .hero-meta .source { color: var(--brand); font-weight: 500; }
        .hero-cta {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 10px 24px;
            background: var(--brand);
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            width: fit-content;
        }
        .hero-cta:hover { background: var(--brand-dark); transform: translateY(-1px); }
        .hero-cta::after { content: "→"; }
        
        /* ===== QUICK NEWS ===== */
        .quick-news {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            background: #fdf8f3;
            padding: 32px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-light);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
        }
        .quick-news-list { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 16px; margin-top: 16px; }
        .quick-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 12px;
            padding: 18px 20px;
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #e8ddd0;
            border-left: 3px solid transparent;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.25s;
        }
        .quick-item:hover { border-left-color: var(--brand); transform: translateX(2px); box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(212,98,42,0.08); }
        .quick-time { font-size: 12px; color: var(--brand); font-weight: 600; flex-shrink: 0; min-width: 48px; }
        .quick-text { font-size: 14px; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; }
        
        /* ===== SECTION TITLE ===== */
        .section-title {
            font-family: "Noto Serif CJK SC", serif;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--text);
            padding-bottom: 12px;
            padding-left: 16px;
            position: relative;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .section-title::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 4px;
            bottom: 4px;
            width: 4px;
            background: var(--brand);
        }
        
        /* ===== NEWS CARDS ===== */
        .main-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px; gap: 48px; margin-bottom: 60px; }
        .news-feed { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }
        
        .news-card {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: 28px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(16px);
            animation: fadeInUp 0.4s forwards;
        }
        .news-card:hover { border-color: var(--brand); box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(212,98,42,0.1); }
        @keyframes fadeInUp { to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
        .news-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.05s; }
        .news-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
        .news-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.15s; }
        .news-card:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
        .news-card:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.25s; }
        .news-card:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
        
        .news-card-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 12px; gap: 16px; }
        .news-card-title { font-family: "Noto Serif CJK SC", serif; font-size: 19px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.5; flex: 1; }
        .news-card-thumb { width: 160px; height: 100px; flex-shrink: 0; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5e6d3, #e8d5c0); }
        .news-card-excerpt { font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .news-card-footer { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
        .news-meta { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; font-size: 12px; color: #999; }
        .news-meta .source { color: var(--brand); font-weight: 500; }
        .news-tags { display: flex; gap: 8px; }
        .tag {
            font-size: 12px;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
        }
        .tag:hover { background: var(--brand); color: #fff; border-color: var(--brand); }
        .tag.hot { background: var(--brand); color: #fff; border-color: var(--brand); }
        
        /* Topic badges */
        .topic-badge { display: inline-block; font-size: 11px; padding: 2px 8px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 6px; }
        .topic-badge.model { background: #EDE9FE; color: #7C3AED; }
        .topic-badge.chip { background: #FEF3C7; color: #D97706; }
        .topic-badge.app { background: #DBEAFE; color: #2563EB; }
        .topic-badge.policy { background: #FEE2E2; color: #DC2626; }
        .topic-badge.research { background: #D1FAE5; color: #059669; }
        .topic-badge.industry { background: #F3E8FF; color: #9333EA; }
        .topic-badge.open { background: #ECFDF5; color: #047857; }
        .topic-badge.deep { background: #FFF7ED; color: #C2410C; }
        .topic-badge.product { background: #EFF6FF; color: #1D4ED8; }
        
        /* ===== SIDEBAR ===== */
        .sidebar { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; border-left: 1px solid #e8ddd0; padding-left: 32px; }
        .sidebar-widget { margin-bottom: 36px; padding-bottom: 28px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light); }
        .sidebar-widget:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .widget-title {
            font-family: "Noto Serif CJK SC", serif;
            font-size: 17px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--text);
            padding-bottom: 12px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--brand);
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .hot-list { list-style: none; }
        .hot-list li { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0ebe4; }
        .hot-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .hot-list li a { text-decoration: none; color: #333; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; transition: color 0.2s; }
        .hot-list li a:hover { color: var(--brand); }
        .hot-rank { font-family: "Noto Serif CJK SC", serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: var(--brand); min-width: 24px; text-align: center; }
        .hot-rank.top3 { color: #D4622A; }
        
        .tag-cloud { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; }
        .tag-cloud .tag { background: #f5f0ea; }
        
        .category-list { list-style: none; }
        .category-list li { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f5f0ea; font-size: 14px; }
        .category-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .category-count { color: var(--brand); font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px; }
        
        /* ===== DEEP DIVE SECTION ===== */
        .deep-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 24px; margin-top: 24px; }
        .deep-card {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            overflow: hidden;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .deep-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); transform: translateY(-2px); }
        .deep-card-img { height: 200px; position: relative; }
        .deep-card-img::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 80px;
            background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(0,0,0,0.4));
        }
        .deep-card-body { padding: 24px; }
        .deep-card-tag { font-size: 11px; color: var(--brand); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .deep-card-title { font-family: "Noto Serif CJK SC", serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        .deep-card-excerpt { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .deep-card-meta { font-size: 12px; color: #999; display: flex; gap: 16px; }
        .deep-card-meta .author { color: var(--brand); font-weight: 500; }
        
        /* ===== PRODUCT SECTION ===== */
        .product-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px; margin-top: 24px; }
        .product-card {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: 28px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            position: relative;
        }
        .product-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); transform: translateY(-2px); }
        .product-card-badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: 16px;
            right: 16px;
            font-size: 11px;
            padding: 3px 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .product-card-badge.new { background: #DCFCE7; color: #166534; }
        .product-card-badge.hot { background: #FEE2E2; color: #DC2626; }
        .product-card-badge.update { background: #DBEAFE; color: #2563EB; }
        .product-icon { font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .product-name { font-family: "Noto Serif CJK SC", serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .product-company { font-size: 13px; color: var(--brand); font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        .product-desc { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .product-stats { display: flex; gap: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #999; }
        .product-stats span { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; }
        
        /* ===== RESEARCH SECTION ===== */
        .research-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; margin-top: 24px; }
        .research-card {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: 28px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 200px;
            gap: 24px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .research-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); border-color: var(--brand); }
        .research-tag { font-size: 11px; padding: 3px 10px; background: #ECFDF5; color: #047857; font-weight: 600; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .research-title { font-family: "Noto Serif CJK SC", serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .research-abstract { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        .research-meta { font-size: 12px; color: #999; display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .research-meta .venue { color: var(--brand); font-weight: 500; }
        .research-thumb { border-radius: 0; overflow: hidden; }
        .research-thumb img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
        
        /* ===== OPENSOURCE SECTION ===== */
        .oss-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 24px; margin-top: 24px; }
        .oss-card {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: 28px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .oss-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); transform: translateY(-2px); }
        .oss-card-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        .oss-name { font-family: "Noto Serif CJK SC", serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; }
        .oss-stars { font-size: 13px; color: #D97706; font-weight: 600; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; }
        .oss-org { font-size: 13px; color: var(--brand); font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .oss-desc { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .oss-tags { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .oss-tag { font-size: 11px; padding: 3px 10px; background: #f5f0ea; color: var(--text-secondary); }
        .oss-stats { display: flex; gap: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #999; }
        
        /* ===== NEWSLETTER ===== */
        .newsletter {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c2c2c 0%, #1a1a1a 100%);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 48px 0;
            margin: 48px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .newsletter h3 { font-family: "Noto Serif CJK SC", serif; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        .newsletter p { color: #999; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
        .newsletter-form { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 12px; max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .newsletter-form input {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border: 1px solid #444;
            background: #333;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .newsletter-form input::placeholder { color: #666; }
        .newsletter-form button {
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background: var(--brand);
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }
        .newsletter-form button:hover { background: var(--brand-dark); }
        
        /* ===== FOOTER ===== */
        footer { background: #1a1a1a; color: #ccc; padding: 56px 0 36px; }
        .footer-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 40px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        .footer-brand .logo { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; display: inline-block; }
        .footer-brand p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.9; color: #999; }
        .footer-col h4 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .footer-col ul { list-style: none; }
        .footer-col ul li { margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .footer-col ul li a { color: #999; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; transition: color 0.2s; }
        .footer-col ul li a:hover { color: var(--brand); }
        .footer-bottom { border-top: 1px solid #333; padding-top: 28px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 12px; color: #555; }
        
        /* Reading progress */
        .reading-progress { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; height: 3px; background: var(--brand); z-index: 1000; transition: width 0.1s; }
        
        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .main-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .sidebar { border-left: none; padding-left: 0; border-top: 1px solid #e8ddd0; padding-top: 32px; flex-direction: row; flex-wrap: wrap; }
            .sidebar-widget { flex: 1; min-width: 280px; }
            .deep-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .product-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
            .oss-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .hero-image { height: 240px; }
            .hero-content { padding: 32px 24px; }
            .hero-title { font-size: 24px; }
            .quick-news-list { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .ticker-bar { display: none; }
            .product-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .research-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .research-thumb { height: 160px; }
            .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
            .section-title { font-size: 19px; }
            nav { gap: 2px; }
            nav a { padding: 8px 10px; font-size: 13px; }
        }
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .header-inner { flex-direction: column; height: auto; padding: 16px 0; gap: 12px; }
            nav { flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
            .news-card-thumb { display: none; }
            .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
        
        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="reading-progress" id="readingProgress"></div>
    
    <!-- Ticker -->
    <div class="ticker-bar">
        <div class="ticker-label">快讯</div>
        <div class="ticker-content" id="tickerContent">
            <span>Anthropic估值9650亿美元启动IPO，成史上最大AI公司</span>
